OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FPlenty of
OL,6,Fshowers lingering into this evening,
OL,7,Fthese could turn heavy at times.
OL,8,FBecoming mostly dry through the early
OL,9,Fhours of the morning with some clear
OL,10,Fspells developing. Lighter winds but a
OL,11,Fcool breeze remains around Welsh
OL,12,Fcoasts.
OL,13,
OL,14,CFriday:FThe odd early shower is
OL,15,Fpossible, otherwise a dry day ahead
OL,16,Fwith light winds and plenty of
OL,17,Fsunshine by the afternoon. Feeling
OL,18,Fless chilly in lighter winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
