OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FMostly
OL,6,Fdry with light winds on Saturday.
OL,7,FShowers possible later but clearing
OL,8,Fthrough Sunday morning. Turning
OL,9,Funsettled later on Monday.
OL,10,FTemperatures returning to near average.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
